# Style Guide Only — No New Elements

**Always use existing design system assets.** Do not introduce new fonts, components, HTML tags, icons, or other elements.

## Fonts

Use only from `src/styles/globals.css` / `src/index.css`:

| Use | Font |
|-----|------|
| Body | Inter (default, 14px base) |
| Display / Headings | IvyPresto Headline (`font-display`) |

```tsx
// ✅ Use Tailwind typography tokens
text-sm text-base text-lg text-xl text-2xl
font-normal font-medium font-semibold font-bold

// ❌ Never add custom font-family or @font-face
font-family: "Some New Font"
```

## Components

Use only from `@/components/ui/` and `@/components/shared/`:

- **Primitives**: Button, Badge, Input, Card, Tabs, Dialog, DropdownMenu, Tooltip, Avatar, Skeleton, Alert, Progress, Switch, Checkbox, Select, Separator, Label, etc.
- **Composites**: PrimaryPageTemplate, ReportPageTemplate, DataTable, FilterBar, MetricCard, SectionWithHeader, etc.

```tsx
// ✅
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
import { Badge } from "@/components/ui/badge";
import { SectionWithHeader } from "@/components/shared/section-with-header";

// ❌ Never create new custom components for basic UI
// ❌ Never use raw HTML for styled elements (e.g. <a> instead of Button with asChild)
```

## Icons

Use only `FontAwesomeIcon` from `@/components/brand/font-awesome-icon` with names from `fontAwesomeIcons`:

```tsx
// ✅
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from "@/components/brand/font-awesome-icon";
<FontAwesomeIcon name="home" />
<FontAwesomeIcon name="bookOpen" weight="solid" />

// ❌ Never use Lucide or other icon libraries as primary
// ❌ Never use inline SVG icons unless from design system
// Need a new icon? Add it to font-awesome-icon.tsx first, then use it.
```

## Tags & Elements

- Use semantic HTML (`div`, `span`, `section`, `header`, etc.) only as wrappers.
- For interactive elements: use `Button`, `Card`, `Badge` — not raw `<button>`, `<a>`, or custom-styled divs.
- For lists: use `DataTable` or existing list patterns — not custom table markup.
- For forms: use `Input`, `Select`, `Checkbox`, `Label` — not raw form elements.

## Design Tokens

- Colors: `bg-primary`, `text-foreground`, `bg-muted`, etc. — never hex or custom colors.
- Spacing: `gap-4`, `p-6`, `px-4 lg:px-6` — from design tokens.
- Radius: `rounded-xl`, `rounded-md`, `rounded-full` — from design tokens.
- **Form fields:** Border `border-[var(--control-border)]`, height `var(--control-height)` — see `docs/design-system/tokens.md`.

```tsx
// ✅
<div className="bg-card text-foreground rounded-xl border border-border p-6" />
<Input className="border-[var(--control-border)]" />  // form fields

// ❌
<div className="bg-[#fff] rounded-[12px]" style={{ padding: 24 }} />
```
